{"lemma":"غَوْرِ","slug":"غَوْرِ","root":"غ.#.ر","root_slug":"غ-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غَوْر","root":"غور","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32606","n32611","n32612"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَارَ (ḡāra) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"depression, sunken place, bottom, low part"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deepness in thought","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"synonym of غَارَ (ḡāra, “to descend, to enter in a state of depression; to seep away”)","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make depressed, to make enter a low position","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to palatalize"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32606","headword_ar":"غوّر","root":"gwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagowiyrN","text_ar":"تَغْوِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, in five places. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slept in the middle of the day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAra","text_ar":"غَارَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He alighted"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to sleep"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the middle of the day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaw~iruwA binaA","text_ar":"غَوِّرُوا بِنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make ye the camels to lie down with us during the vehement midday-heat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jm and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rmD","text_ar":"رمض"},{"kind":"text","text":".) IAar says that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugaw~irN","text_ar":"مُغَوِّرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"alighting in the middle of the day for a little while and then departing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resuming his journey"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bit~u h`*ihi All~ayolapa A_il~aA tagowiyrFA","text_ar":"مَا بِتُّ هٰذِهِ اللَّيْلَةَ اـِلَّا تَغْوِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad. as meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did not tarry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have not tarried, this night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save in taking a nap"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the sleep in the middle of the day"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He entered upon the middle of the day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He journeyed in the middle of the day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a rider upon a camel, or upon a horse or other beast,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeyed until the declining of the sun from the meridian, and then alighted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gw~r Aln~ahaAru","text_ar":"غوّر النَّهَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day became intensely hot when"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sun declined from the meridian."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-Buzurj, TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAra Aln~ahaAru","text_ar":"غَارَ النَّهَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gw~rhu","text_ar":"غوّرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it to enter, into a low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, place: he hid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused it to disappear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 165.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gw~r","text_ar":"غوّر"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n. as above, (K, TA,) signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He routed, defeated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put to flight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he drove away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n32611","headword_ar":"غَوْرٌ","root":"gwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything; (S, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaworaY","text_ar":"غَوْرَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earafotu gawora h`*ihi AlmasoA^alapi","text_ar":"عَرَفْتُ غَوْرَ هٰذِهِ المَسْاَلَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have become acquainted with the bottom of this question"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN baEiydu Algawori","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ بَعِيدُ الغَوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is deep and excellent in judgment; one who examines deeply."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also 1.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawa baHorN laA yudoraku gaworuhu","text_ar":"هَوَ بَحْرٌ لَا يُدْرَكُ غَوْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is a sea whereof the bottom shall not be reached"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano","text_ar":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboEadu gaworFA fiY AlbaATili min~iY","text_ar":"اَبْعَدُ غَوْرًا فِى البَاطِلِ مِنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Who is deeper in knowledge with respect to what is vain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"false, than I?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA, from a trad.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, land, country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaworN","text_ar":"خَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaArN","text_ar":"غَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaArN","text_ar":"غَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the first of its senses expl. above.       -A2-  Applied to water,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAy^irN","text_ar":"غَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sinking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going away, into the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:) an inf. n. used as an epithet, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N sakobN","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ سَكْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirohamN DarobN","text_ar":"دِرْهَمٌ ضَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n32612","headword_ar":"غِوَرٌ","root":"gwr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bloodwit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyapN","text_ar":"دِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giyarN","text_ar":"غِيَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or the latter is a pl., of which the sing. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giyrapN","text_ar":"غِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AA, K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gyr","text_ar":"غير"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}